data.value: Get acquainted with the document. If you are going to take vacations as scheduled, click "Confirm" and sign the document. Some vacation periods are scheduled without working days between them. If you want to change the vacation periods, contact your direct manager or go to the "Applications" section and create an "Other Application". In such case, do not complete this assignment and close the confirmation window.
